[SHORT DESC]
Cures status on the user's team.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Cures burn, confusion, freeze, paralysis, poison, and sleep from every Pokémon on the user's team. It works even if a Soundproof Pokémon is out, but it doesn't heal any Pokémon in the user's party that have the ability Soundproof.
</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/moves/aromatherapy">Aromatherapy</a> is almost identical, but is not blocked by <a href="/rs/abilites/sounrsroof">Soundproof</a>.</p>